name: Grilled Lobster
description: Indulge in our exquisite Grilled Lobster, a sumptuous delicacy expertly grilled to perfection and served with a rich garlic butter sauce that enhances its natural sweetness.

name: Tuna Steak
description: Experience the freshness of our Tuna Steak, carefully seared to retain its natural flavors and moisture, seasoned to perfection with a blend of herbs.

name: Caesar Salad
description: Our Caesar Salad is a vibrant mix of crisp romaine lettuce tossed with a creamy Caesar dressing, crunchy croutons, and grated parmesan cheese.

name: Bruschetta
description: Toasted bread topped with fresh tomatoes, basil, and mozzarella, our Bruschetta is a delightful starter bursting with flavor.

name: Vegan Burger
description: Our Vegan Burger features a delicious plant-based patty, topped with fresh vegetables and creamy avocado for a healthy, satisfying meal.

name: Mango Smoothie
description: Refreshing and creamy, our Mango Smoothie is blended with yogurt and honey for a tropical treat that's perfect for any time of day.

name: Pepperoni Pizza
description: Our Pepperoni Pizza is a classic favorite, topped with generous slices of pepperoni, gooey mozzarella cheese, and a rich tomato sauce.

name: Chocolate Lava Cake
description: Decadent and indulgent, our Chocolate Lava Cake features a molten chocolate center that flows out with each bite, served warm for maximum delight.

name: Chicken Satay
description: Grilled to perfection, our Chicken Satay skewers are served with a creamy peanut sauce that adds a delightful contrast of flavors.

name: Tiramisu
description: This classic Italian dessert is made of layers of coffee-soaked ladyfingers and rich mascarpone cheese, making it a perfect end to any meal.

name: Espresso Martini
description: A perfect blend of espresso and vodka, our Espresso Martini is topped with coffee beans for an elegant touch that coffee lovers will adore.

name: Iced Americano
description: Chilled and refreshing, our Iced Americano is a smooth coffee beverage that captures the rich flavor of espresso with a cool twist.

name: Salmon Sashimi
description: Enjoy fresh slices of salmon served with soy sauce and wasabi, perfect for sashimi lovers seeking a high-quality, authentic experience.

name: French Fries
description: Our French Fries are crispy and golden, the perfect side dish for dipping in your favorite sauces or enjoying on their own.

name: Green Curry
description: Spicy and aromatic, our Green Curry is made with fresh vegetables and coconut milk for a comforting and flavorful meal.

name: Mashed Potatoes
description: Creamy and buttery, our Mashed Potatoes are seasoned with herbs for a comforting side that pairs well with any main course.

name: Spaghetti Carbonara
description: Delight in our Spaghetti Carbonara, a classic Italian pasta dish tossed with eggs, cheese, pancetta, and pepper for a rich and savory flavor.

name: Garlic Bread
description: Toasted bread spread with garlic butter, our Garlic Bread is an irresistible side that complements any meal with its aromatic flavor.

name: Orange Juice
description: Freshly squeezed from the best oranges, our Orange Juice is a refreshing drink that captures the bright and tangy flavor of the fruit.

name: Panna Cotta
description: Our Panna Cotta is a creamy dessert topped with a luscious berry sauce, offering a perfect blend of sweetness and creaminess in every bite.
